                  <interp inst="t18310908-102-crimeloc569" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-102-off566 t18310908-102-crimeloc569"></join>. This time-piece was near the window on the 24th of August- as I came down stairs I saw the prisoner going off the step of the door with it in his hand; I pursued about a hundred yards, calling Stop thief! I then lost sight of him as he put it down, and ran away - I took it up, and returned home; the Policeman brought him back soon after - I did not see his face, but have not a doubt of him; he was the same size, and wore the same dress - the parasol laid on a side-board in the passage.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-102-person892">
